Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libpsocksxx0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: A C++ wrapper for POSIX sockets
 psocksxx is a C++ wrapper for POSIX sockets implemented by extending
 the STL stream classes (e.g. std::streambuf, std::istream etc.).
 .
 This package contains the development files for psocksxx library.

